page.title: 20A DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content: I wake up at{7.30am}and get ready for school.I have breakfast, then I brush my teeth and wash.I leave for school at{8.30am}.I play in the playground until{9.00am}.I work until{10.30am doing maths.When I go out I play football until{10.45am}. I work again until{12.10pm.}For dinner have a meat course or salad and vegetables.I play football until{1.15pm.}I come in and work until{2.30pm.}I play football until{2.45pm}.I come in and read until {3.10pm}.Then my teacher reads a story until{3.30pm}. I put my chair up and go home.I have my tea and play out until{9.00pm}.watch t.v. until {9.30pm}.I brush my teeth and wash my face and hands then I go to bed.
